==English==

===Etymology===
From the act of [[tying]] or even [[nail]]ing a pigeon to a stool to act as a [[decoy]] for hunters.

=== Noun ===
'''[[stool]] [[pigeon]]'''
# {{slang}} A decoy or an [[informer]], especially one who is a [[spy]] for the police.

===Translations===
*Russian: [[наседка]] (brood hen), [[подсадная утка]]

